  "title": "ARCHITECTURAL DESIGNER",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Work closely with Client, Local consultants, PM, Constructors, Suppliers, Quantity surveyor based on the knowledge and experience of Architectural and Structural design.</li><li>Preparation of presentations throughout the phase of design development by creating 3d rendered images and initial floor plans.</li><li>To perform detail design: Detail design development (drawings and specifications)</li><li>Tender document preparation (tender design brief, scope demarcation)</li><li>To perform construction phase design: Review of construction material / shop drawing</li><li>Shop drawing preparation (with drafter), coordination and obtain approval from client or local consultant</li><li>Periodical site inspection (internal check for quality improvement)</li><li>Verify site installation works are according to design intent.</li><li>To liaise with PE's, builders, clients and suppliers all throughout the project lifecycle.</li><li>Handover submission arrangement with drafter team and project team</li></ul><p><u><strong>Qualifications:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Bachelor’s Degree in Architecture or a related field.</li><li>At least 5 years of relevant experience in residential / A&A development projects.</li><li>Familiarity with local regulations and experience in authority submissions.</li><li>Strong technical knowledge and attention to detail.</li><li>Proficiency in Revit, AutoCAD, Lumion, SketchUp, Photoshop, and 3Ds Max.</li><li>Recognise by Singapore Board of Architect</li><li>Qualified to be TC</li></ul><p><strong>Other information:</strong></p><p>• Central East, Singapore</p><p>• Monday to Friday</p><p>You may also email your resume to hr@sevensbuild.com</p>",
